headline: 3 Manufacturing Tools Stocks to Watch Despite Industry Headwinds
summary: The prospects of the Zacks Manufacturing-Tools & Related Products industry are hindered by persistent weakness in the manufacturing sector and ongoing supply-chain challenges. LECO, SWK and EPAC are a few stocks investors should retain.
